{"tid":1149421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡法當前，請放下派別之爭，大局為重","createTime":"2019-05-11T06:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T09:10:15.000Z","uid":95,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc831d0a5fc3ad5694ebc8560fdf0e5bd62457f1","tid":1149421,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"頂完條惡法先再慢慢互屌啦，而家真係無分裂既本錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白飯民過去係做過好多仆街野，但而家唯一可以係議會入面幫到香港人既就只有佢地。現實政治角度睇，借用佢地既力量對抗惡法先係明智。遲啲立法會選舉再屌佢地啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338b6e961c0ab9847e2f939055c8fa702844901a","tid":1149421,"uid":76471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n<br />\n佔領立法會點睇？"},{"pid":"b4a95ef8d6c3aeb60fe77e70de367d85555aadec","tid":1149421,"uid":60381,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"應該好快又有私怨撚入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你香港人永遠唔識團結"},{"pid":"432ac61fa375d9e762add13cad5f7ad678a457c9","tid":1149421,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"338b6e961c0ab9847e2f939055c8fa702844901a","tid":1149421,"uid":76471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n<br />\n佔領立法會點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"睇形勢啦"},{"pid":"7109af3ff9ae59dc25fc7206722511a57b7519be","tid":1149421,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a95ef8d6c3aeb60fe77e70de367d85555aadec","tid":1149421,"uid":60381,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"應該好快又有私怨撚入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你香港人永遠唔識團結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:05:14.000Z","msg":"借力打力都要啦，根本立法會入面係要靠佢地。"},{"pid":"1fd8232f3b39bbd7620bfb77111a04571c9cfa07","tid":1149421,"uid":82482,"like":9,"dislike":1